
<div class="card card-outline-primary m-1 p-1 rounded text-center text-primary">
    <div class="bg-faded p-1">
        <span class="badge badge-primary w-100">
            <h2> About Me </h2>
        </span>
        <p style="padding:40px 100px">
            Hello! My name is Priscilla and I am a software engineer, military veteran,
            and dog enthusiast! Throughout my life, I have always been passionate about
            animals. My love for dogs started when I got my very own puppy! Winnie is a
            border collie from England, and is my inspiration for HealthyPUP. I wanted to
            give Winnie the best life possible, and I realized I wanted to track every
            aspect of it. So came the idea of HealthyPUP. HealthyPUP allows users to record
            all aspects of their fur baby's life, to include their diet, exercise, medical
            records, and more! This will empower users by spotting early detection of health
            issues and see how new foods can impact their pup. I hope HealthyPUP can help you
            keep your fur babies healthy!
        </p>
        <!--Carousel-->
        <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide col-6 offset-3" data-ride="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://i.ibb.co/Cnm0fdQ/winnie.jpg" alt="First slide">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://i.ibb.co/jf5T1p1/winnie.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://i.ibb.co/LPqRZd8/pub.jpg" alt="Third slide">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://i.ibb.co/fp4m3Lr/baby.png" alt="Fourth slide">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://i.ibb.co/LnGW3Jg/IMG-2710.jpg" alt="Fifth slide">
                </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
            <br/>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


